Fair fa' your honest, sonsie face,<br />
Great chieftain o' the puddin-race!<br />
Aboon them a' ye tak your place,<br />
Painch, tripe, or thairm:<br />
Weel are ye wordy o' a grace<br />
As lang's my arm.<br />
<br />
